'''庇護五世'''（{{lang-es|Pío Quinto}}）是一種[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]的傳統[[聖誕蛋糕|聖誕蛋糕]]，製作方法是將浸透[[朗姆酒|朗姆酒]]的蛋糕澆蓋一層[[卡士達醬|卡士達醬]]，再撒上[[肉桂|肉桂粉]]而成<ref name=Pio>{{cite book | title = A World of Cake  | author= Krystina Castella | publisher = Storey Publishing |url = https://books.google.com/?id=Z20XOWapBCEC&pg=PA60&dq=%22Pio+Quinto%22+-wikipedia#v=onepage&q=%22Pio%20Quinto%22%20-wikipedia&f=false | date = 2012 | pages = 60 and 74| isbn = 9781603424462  | access-date = 6 May 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=MARÍA DEL MAR CUADRA |title=Pío V (Nicaraguan Christmas Cake) Recipe |url=https://www.seriouseats.com/recipes/2011/12/dulces-pio-v-nicaraguan-christmas-cake-rum-custard-recipe.html |website=SERIOUS EATS |accessdate=2021-01-13 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416072306/https://www.seriouseats.com/recipes/2011/12/dulces-pio-v-nicaraguan-christmas-cake-rum-custard-recipe.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；有時候會還加入[[葡萄乾|葡萄乾]]。

這種甜點是以[[教宗庇護五世|教宗庇護五世]]命名的，但確切的原因已不可考<ref name=Pio/><ref>{{cite web |title=Pio quinto |url=https://www.tasteatlas.com/pio-quinto |website=https://www.tasteatlas.com/ |accessdate=2021-01-13 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023015943/https://www.tasteatlas.com/pio-quinto |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

